      <title>养老基金预计在季度末出售 320 亿美元股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/pension-funds-seen-selling-32-billion-of-stock-into-quarter-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 表示，随着股市将迎来又一个强劲的季度，养老基金可能会出售估计 320 亿美元的股票以重新平衡其头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/pension-funds-seen-selling-32-billion-of-stock-into-quarter-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
