      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 08:07:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于政策驱动的反弹动摇，中国股市抹去了三月份的涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/chinese-stocks-erase-march-gains-as-policy-driven-rally-falters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市回吐了 3 月份的涨幅，原因是业绩令人失望，削弱了人们对 2 月份开始的政策驱动反弹的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/chinese-stocks-erase-march-gains-as-policy-driven-rally-falters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 08:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Old Mutual 将斥资 1.34 亿美元创办新南非银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/-exceptional-business-growth-drives-old-mutual-profit-up-35</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非资产最大的保险公司 Old Mutual Ltd. 计划在 2024 年底前在南非推出新银行，此前这家非洲大陆资产规模最大的保险公司从其董事会获得了对该项目的进一步资助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/-exceptional-business-growth-drives-old-mutual-profit-up-35</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 06:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元跌至 1990 年以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yen-drops-to-lowest-since-1990-amid-intervention-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日元兑美元汇率跌至约 34 年来的最低水平，日本发出迄今为止最强烈​​的警告，距离货币干预又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yen-drops-to-lowest-since-1990-amid-intervention-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 02:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市小幅走低，日元从 34 年低点反弹：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者寻求推动市场走高的催化剂，欧洲股市在欧元区新数据公布前下跌。由于干预押注不断增加，日元兑美元汇率触及 1990 年以来的最低水平后反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DS Smith 在美国谈判引发竞购战前景后股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/ds-smith-confirms-talks-with-international-paper-on-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DS Smith Plc 确认与美国竞争对手国际纸业公司 (International Paper Co.) 进行谈判后股价攀升，引发了对这家英国包装公司可能的竞购战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/ds-smith-confirms-talks-with-international-paper-on-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
